{"tid":996496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[扣你200紋] 羅致光：60至64歲綜援受助人不參加自力更生者扣200元只是「象徵式」，對長者不大影響","createTime":"2019-01-26T10:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T07:34:17.000Z","uid":56321,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"79756810253273ce22857f72ec4695dee4198ad4","tid":996496,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"羅致光：不參加自力更生者扣200元是放寬要求<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=335536&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D335536%26refer%3DShare&d=M3ZqFwR%2B202pwTicjjMYPgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=1885e5dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D335536%26refer%3DShare&h=3fa62d01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=335536&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】60至64歲綜援受助人不參加自力更生就業援助計劃，社會福利署會每月扣200元就業支援補助金。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，有關安排是「放寬」要求，形容二百元只是「象徵式」，相信不會影響大部分人。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光：「昨天與社福機構交代的，是我們如何放寬要求，不是收緊要求，大家不要誤會。有象徵式的東西如果連象徵式的都沒有，當然變成了所謂的自願性，但是大家都知道大部分人都很自願性去工作，所以有少少象徵式要求，我覺得是合理的，我相信絕大部分人不會受到這件事影響。」"},{"pid":"8af95b4425aa54caa78b8517852ae384f70c90e3","tid":996496,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"張建宗：扣200元措施鼓勵長者站起來<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=335566&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D335566%26refer%3DShare&d=M3ZqFwR%2B202pwTicjjMYPgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=1b628eaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D335566%26refer%3DShare&h=cb08c18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=335566&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】下月起，60至64歲綜援受助人假如半年無求職，會被扣200元綜援金額。政務司司長張建宗指，<strong>措施不是迫長者「搵工」，而是鼓勵他們「站起來」。</strong>勞工及福利局局長羅致光就形容二百元只是「象徵式」，不會影響大部分人。<br />\n<br />\n下月起，長者綜援的申領年齡調高至65歲，60至64歲的健全綜援受助人可選擇參加自力更生就業支援計劃。假如連續三次都缺席和社工面談，將會被扣減二百元綜援金額。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，措施不是<strong>懲罰長者</strong>，而是<strong>鼓勵他們求職</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他年齡參加自力更生計劃的人士，假如達不到會面次數要求，會被扣減兩星期的綜援金。<br />\n<br />\n勞工福利局局長羅致光認為，二百元是合理的象徵式要求，影響人數亦不多。<strong>IQ160羅致光又指，上班對大部分人來說，對精神健康及社交都有好處。</strong>"},{"pid":"643fe2e1bfaa170753d399cd1fab8462d094470f","tid":996496,"uid":173598,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"09e472e24a45af88e8596cf583e6c984fd41c4af","tid":996496,"uid":20816,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"「對精神健康及社交都有好處」?<br />\n日日夜夜俾人屌老母老豆"},{"pid":"cee89f89e92e1126858a6276ed7178eecb31a829","tid":996496,"uid":10757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"象徵式咁姐係多餘喇 咁你又收... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf4eef43a99d0e3b97957068e9c92a42376f8e1","tid":996496,"uid":7961,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"不如有搵到工，俾兩百仲正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641101ba0712e2ed45bad981ddd2a4795105b6cd","tid":996496,"uid":115306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"呢種咁反智同無理既政策係咪香港獨有"},{"pid":"63ba8da29b4d1a40600f5a11b5f5061f33d465d9","tid":996496,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"假設綜援嗰班蝗上面有啲錢，或者打散工社署嘅，你扣佢二百真係無傷大雅<br />\n<br />\n但真係做唔到嘢嗰班，做得嘅就唔駛攞綜援，做唔到嘅無啦啦比你扣二百<br />\n<br />\n站得起來做嘢就唔駛攞綜援啦狗官，你比